Release details, version LTS.411
Patch LTS.411.3 of May 21, 2024
Changes and improvements
Print forms optimizations and updates in the Edoc module;
Stabilizations in document opening with an incorrectly deleted object in the Edoc module.
Patch LTS.411.2 of May 20, 2024
Changes and improvements
"Dependent objects" button display settings were optimized.
Update package LTS.411.1 of May 17, 2024
New features
1. “Dependent objects” button added to control panel: it allows viewing objects used to current object.
2. Registries now show employees working on profile:
Changes and improvements
Working with permission groups was improved;
Excel filters in dashboards were improved;
Working with ETL diagram was optimized;
Folder registry hierarchy was stabilized;
Operation of "Theme designer" was improved;
Working with
"Task list" widget
for was improved;
Display of values in "Object registry" and "Reporting form" was stabilized;
Using filters in "Authorization subject" object type was improved;
Interaction of
"Kanban board"
with other dashboards was stabilized;
Working with
parentAttr
function was stabilized;
Route objects condition was optimized;
Creating template instances was stabilized;
Edoc improvements: generating files using exportEDoc function was optimized.
